//Improtant of xml file to run multiple test case  
  1. Create Xml  file : RightClick > TestNg > Convert To Test NG
  2. To exectue test suite
     Right click on xml  file > Run as  > TestNG Suite
  3. Include and excludefro specific requirement in excel file


 // HOw To Run tests testing ?
 
   You need to have @Test annotation followed by method 
 
   you can define multiple tests from single class
 
   you can modularize the testcases based up on functionality and trigger them accordingly
 
You can learn more about TestngXML suite structure from below link

